{"tid":1811121,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中大拓展及籌募處長宿舍上吊亡","createTime":"2020-01-04T11:54:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-05T02:18:30.000Z","uid":51271,"like":10,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"5bbf2163abbee5e61cba8280d28430d8c2e35a72","tid":1811121,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T11:54:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200104/s00001/1578130870246/%e4%b8%ad%e5%a4%a7%e6%8b%93%e5%b1%95%e5%8f%8a%e7%b1%8c%e5%8b%9f%e8%99%95%e9%95%b7%e5%ae%bf%e8%88%8d%e4%b8%8a%e5%90%8a%e4%ba%a1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200104%2Fs00001%2F1578130870246%2F%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e5%25a4%25a7%25e6%258b%2593%25e5%25b1%2595%25e5%258f%258a%25e7%25b1%258c%25e5%258b%259f%25e8%2599%2595%25e9%2595%25b7%25e5%25ae%25bf%25e8%2588%258d%25e4%25b8%258a%25e5%2590%258a%25e4%25ba%25a1&d=x%2FFuRRgY0RqQB1T9iHKuLQjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=f2efcac6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200104%2Fs00001%2F1578130870246%2F%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e5%25a4%25a7%25e6%258b%2593%25e5%25b1%2595%25e5%258f%258a%25e7%25b1%258c%25e5%258b%259f%25e8%2599%2595%25e9%2595%25b7%25e5%25ae%25bf%25e8%2588%258d%25e4%25b8%258a%25e5%2590%258a%25e4%25ba%25a1&h=bff7f837\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200104/s00001/1578130870246/%e4%b8%ad%e5%a4%a7%e6%8b%93%e5%b1%95%e5%8f%8a%e7%b1%8c%e5%8b%9f%e8%99%95%e9%95%b7%e5%ae%bf%e8%88%8d%e4%b8%8a%e5%90%8a%e4%ba%a1</a><br />\n<br />\n昨日（3日）下午5時許，一名50歲女子在中文大學一間職員宿舍內以尼龍繩上吊，其19歲女兒發現時大驚，自行將母親解下並報警。救護員接報到場，女子昏迷送往威爾斯親王醫院治理，其後證實死亡。警方於現場沒有檢獲遺書，初步調查後相信事件沒有可疑，死因有待驗屍後確定。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>多名中大消息人士向本報確認，死者為中大拓展及籌募處處長周瑤慧。據悉，她近日受工作壓力及家庭問題困擾。</strong><br />\n<br />\n中大發言人表示，對於同事離世感到難過，向其家人致以深切慰問，會盡力提供適切協助，同時會為有需要的同事提供情緒支援。<br />\n<br />\n周瑤慧80年代於中大電子計算學系畢業，再完成中大工商管理碩士課程。她前年12月接受《崇基校園通訊》訪問時，稱自己和丈夫近年在崇基聖誕兒童聯歡中扮演「聖誕老人伉儷」，有「聖誕老婆」之稱。"},{"pid":"6541b1cedfab5740b95054a9d54ac4bc69318322","tid":1811121,"uid":259010,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T11:55:41.000Z","msg":"死黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c743963580a7a81346af18aa221654d04fb789b3","tid":1811121,"uid":71508,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T11:56:57.000Z","msg":"佢個女好慘"},{"pid":"0163c743bc10de99981db0bb697d1d9fc0e98ee6","tid":1811121,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T11:58:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nRIP"},{"pid":"b5cca47e8a45684d023e6a42fdca7172064c0fcc","tid":1811121,"uid":103916,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T12:05:19.000Z","msg":"死黑警"},{"pid":"3c7e78f0abb938058ef172c0605d8e9b0d0afe9e","tid":1811121,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T12:09:46.000Z","msg":"推到比立場/蘋果/議員睇到<br />\n［停止使用建制稱呼親共人士］<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZQscQho.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZQscQho.jpg&h=56da94ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n強烈要求使用「共派」取代「建制」稱呼<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1811104\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1811104</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9ab215438628e0b5b5e5e849b70f2f4813298419","tid":1811121,"uid":126053,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T12:10:02.000Z","msg":"中大人會幫你行埋落去"},{"pid":"b494a962fae16ae2809991efeacb6d9a97fc47c4","tid":1811121,"uid":81385,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T12:12:36.000Z","msg":"屌你老母政府<br />\n鬼叫你出哂江湖追殺令封殺中大<br />\ncampus比你打爆左<br />\n又收番撥款<br />\n仲要邊個捐大筆錢比中大就比稅局查比狗玩<br />\n屌你老母"},{"pid":"7da66bb87f52049c53868a2570d63cdd79ae5a82","tid":1811121,"uid":87745,